Context: The Library Learning Commons (LLC) at George Brown College provides research support, academic resources, and tech help. Their website can be accessed at <https://www.georgebrown.ca/library-learning-commons>. They offer orientation presentations and digital goodies on their site, which can be found by visiting the "Orientation Presentations" or "Fun Stuff" sections. The URL for library events is bit.ly/gbclibraryevents.
